title: Witness against Hong Kong media mogul was mistreated, Post examination finds
description:
Former Hong Kong democracy activist Andy Li, a key witness in the trial of media mogul Jimmy Lai, was mistreated in 
prison in China, a Post examination finds

title: Israel-Gaza live war updates: Thousands protest in Israel after IDF kills 3 hostages in Gaza
description: Protesters in Tel Aviv called for Israel to negotiate the release of all hostages after the IDF mistakenly killed three hostages carrying a white flag in Gaza.

title: Gaza, smashed by rockets and bombs, sees new threat: Disease
description: After 10 weeks of war, the besieged enclave is now fertile ground for the spread of pathogens. Staph infections, chickenpox meningitis and scabies are all rising.

title: Biden’s support of Israel could come at a cost to U.S. foreign policy
description: America’s partners and allies are increasingly frustrated that the United States isn’t using its leverage to protect Palestinian lives.
